lead_paragraph: Resurgent Red Bull replaced Ferrari as the best-of-the-rest behind Mercedes after racing to their first double-podium in over a year in Sunday's German Formula One Grand Prix.

headline.print_headline: Red Bull Best-Of-The-Rest After Double German GP Podium
